00:01.174 --> 00:02.241
<i>Dear Journal,</i>

00:02.275 --> 00:04.043
<i>it's Christmas again...</i>

00:04.077 --> 00:06.045
<i>that time of year</i>
<i>when parents aren't arrested</i>

00:06.079 --> 00:07.513
<i>for forcing their children to sit</i>

00:07.547 --> 00:10.249
<i>on an old man's weirdly hot lap.</i>

00:10.283 --> 00:14.653
<i>That magical season when five</i>
<i>seemingly separate storylines</i>

00:14.688 --> 00:18.323
<i>are cleverly sandwiched</i>
<i>between commercial breaks,</i>

00:18.358 --> 00:22.394
<i>and then tied together at</i>
<i>the end like a beautiful bow.</i>

00:22.429 --> 00:25.097
<i>Like that movie</i> Love, Actually.

00:25.131 --> 00:27.666
<i>Which I don't think anyone</i>
<i>really cares for,</i>

00:27.701 --> 00:30.803
<i>and yet it is constantly on cable.</i>

